Videos.Title: Floridas gator / snake filled DEATH ZONE and secret swamp silos
Videos.Description:
www.AdamTheWoo.com - PLEASE SUBSCRIBE !  - Armed with a few bottles of h2o, a beach cruiser and a little sunblock I embarked on the most dangerous adventure to date. This video in no way does this place justice. The fear of god was put in me on more than one occasion. What the video doesnt show is the incredible amount of gators in the water and on land, so close you could touch them. 
It took me 3 tries to climb the silo, shown by alternate cuts in the video,youll even notice me chicken out in one of the shots. As the day progressed I ran out of battery life and could film no more. On the route back we practically passed out from heat exaustion with sun burns to follow. 
I wouldnt wish this adventure on anyone, its harsh ! Almost a 20 mile round trip bike ride thru the swamp.

Videos.Title: Real Life Snow White Cottage - Disneyland Inspiration ?
Videos.Description:
http://www.AdamTheWoo.com - PLEASE SUBSCRIBE - A replica of the Snow White cottage and wishing well , seven dwarfs mine shaft and witches hut were built in 1938 on Gamble Place at spruce creek . Located in Port Orange Florida the structures were created as an homage to the fantastic Disney film. Walt Disney himself paid visit to the property long before the idea of Disneyland came about. This relatively secret spot has an incredible story. Enjoy !
